<p>on the verge of : ~의 경계에 있으므로 뭔가 변화가 일어나기 직전.</p>

<p>                       막 ~ 하려고 하는 중인.</p>

<p>ex)</p>

<p>The country was on the verge of becoming prosperous and successful.</p>

<p>Carole was on the verge of tears.</p>

